#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:72
#, fuzzy
msgid "How to troubleshoot a failed installation."
msgstr ""
"如何排除安装失败的问题。\n"
"\n"
" Troubleshooting a failed installation typically involves identifying the root cause of the issue and implementing corrective actions. Here are some general steps to help you troubleshoot a failed installation:\n"
"\n"
"1. Check system requirements: Verify that your system meets all the necessary hardware and software requirements for the installation. Make sure your operating system, processor, memory, and disk space are compatible and sufficient.\n"
"\n"
"2. Review error messages: Look for any error messages or codes displayed during the installation process. These messages can provide valuable information about the cause of the failure. Search for these error messages online for possible solutions.\n"
"\n"
"3. Check installation logs: Most software installations generate logs that record the installation process. Review these logs to identify any errors or warnings that occurred during the installation. These logs can be found in the installation directory or in the system's event viewer.\n"
"\n"
"4. Update software: Make sure you are using the latest version of the software you are trying to install. Sometimes, older versions may have compatibility issues with your system.\n"
"\n"
"5. Disable security software: Temporarily disable any antivirus or firewall software on your system. Sometimes, these security programs can interfere with the installation process. Once the installation is complete, remember to re-enable your security software.\n"
"\n"
"6. Clean up previous installations: If you have previously attempted to install the software, make sure to completely uninstall it before trying a new installation. Lingering remnants of a previous installation can cause conflicts and lead to failures.\n"
"\n"
"7. Use administrator privileges: Run the installation as an administrator. Right-click on the installation file and select \"Run as Administrator\" to ensure that the installation has the necessary permissions to modify system files and settings.\n"
"\n"
"8. Consult the documentation: Check the installation guide or documentation provided by the software vendor for specific troubleshooting steps. They may have documented common issues and their resolutions.\n"
"\n"
"9. Contact support: If you have exhausted all troubleshooting steps and still cannot resolve the installation failure, reach out to the software vendor's support team for assistance. Provide them with detailed information about the issue, including any error messages or logs.\n"
"\n"
"通过识别问题的根本原因并执行纠正措施，通常可以排除安装失败的问题。以下是一些通用的步骤，可帮助您排除安装失败的问题：\n"
"\n"
"1. 检查系统要求：验证您的系统是否符合安装所需的所有硬件和软件要求。确保您的操作系统、处理器、内存和磁盘空间兼容并足够。\n"
"\n"
"2. 查看错误消息：在安装过程中查找任何显示的错误消息或代码。这些消息可以提供有关失败原因的有用信息。在网上搜索这些错误消息，以寻找可能的解决方案。\n"
"\n"
"3. 检查安装日志：大多数软件安装都会生成记录安装过程的日志。查看这些日志，以确定安装过程中是否出现了任何错误或警告。这些日志可以在安装目录或系统的事件查看器中找到。\n"
"\n"
"4. 更新软件：确保您使用的是要安装的软件的最新版本。有时，旧版本可能与您的系统存在兼容性问题。\n"
"\n"
"5. 禁用安全软件：临时禁用系统中的任何防病毒或防火墙软件。有时，这些安全程序可能会干扰安装过程。安装完成后，请记得重新启用安全软件。\n"
"\n"
"6. 清理先前的安装：如果您之前曾尝试过安装该软件，请在尝试新的安装之前将其彻底卸载。先前安装的残留部分可能会导致冲突并导致失败。\n"
"\n"
"7. 使用管理员权限：以管理员身份运行安装。右键单击安装文件，然后选择“以管理员身份运行”，以确保安装具有修改系统文件和设置的必要权限。\n"
"\n"
"8. 查阅文档：检查软件供应商提供的安装指南或文档，了解具体的故障排除步骤。他们可能已经记录了常见问题及其解决方法。\n"
"\n"
"9. 联系支持：如果您已经尝试了所有的故障排除步骤，仍然无法解决安装失败的问题，请联系软件供应商的支持团队寻求帮助。向他们提供详细的问题信息，包括任何错误消息或日志。"

