#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:146
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Although the FreeBSD Project strives to ensure that each release of FreeBSD "
"is as stable as possible, bugs occasionally creep into the process.  On very"
" rare occasions those bugs affect the installation process.  As these "
"problems are discovered and fixed, they are noted in the FreeBSD Errata page"
" of each version.  Check the errata before installing to make sure that "
"there are no problems that might affect the installation."
msgstr ""
"尽管 FreeBSD 项目努力确保每个版本的 FreeBSD "
"尽可能稳定，但偶尔会出现一些错误。在极少数情况下，这些错误会影响安装过程。随着这些问题的发现和修复，它们会在每个版本的 FreeBSD "
"勘误页面中进行记录。在安装之前，请检查勘误，以确保没有可能影响安装的问题。"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:148
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Information and errata for all the releases can be found on the "
"link:https://www.FreeBSD.org/releases/[FreeBSD Release Information] page."
msgstr ""
"所有发布版本的信息和勘误信息可以在链接：https://www.FreeBSD.org/releases/[ FreeBSD发布信息] 页面找到。"

#. type: Title ===
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:151
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Prepare the Installation Media"
